									<h2>What Is Blast3D?</h2>
									<p>Blast3D is an easy to learn, game development language with its Blitz3D origins. It is continued to be used by many game developers worldwide, in a large part due to the continually active developer community.</p>
									<br>
									<h2>3D Everywhere</h2>
